IonoObservationAmplitude_Ingest.description: /// Multi-dimensional array with the same dimensions as power plus one additional dimension antenna_element. This variable is enabled for post-process polarization or antenna array determination. Can be combined with phase to create a phasors and subsequently enable post-processing of polarization and/or antenna array determination.

notes.description:
Notes for the amplitude data.
Example: /// Example: NOTES
Constraints: Minimum length = 0, Maximum length = 512

dimensions.description:
Array of integers for amplitude dimensions.
Example: /// Example: [4, 5]
Constraints: No constraints specified.

dimensionName.description:
Array of names for dimensions.
Example: /// Example: ['NAME1', 'NAME2']
Constraints: No constraints specified.

data.description:
Array of amplitude data.
Example: /// Example: [[[[[[[0.02, 0.034]]]]]]]
Constraints: No constraints specified.
